  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Studying in the European Union after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Advice for students and citizens who want to start or continue higher education study in any European Union (EU) country after the UK leaves the EU.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

